.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
Transport: boat, bus, airplane, scooter
Food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. Food:artichoke is on the far right##1
2. Transport:bus is somewhere to the left of Transport:airplane##5
3. Food:onion is somewhere to the left of Transport:scooter##5
4. Transport:bus != Food:grapefruit##6
5. Food:onion is on the left of Transport:airplane##1
6. Food:artichoke is on the right of Food:lettuce##1
7. Transport:scooter is on the right of Transport:boat##1
8. Transport:airplane is somewhere to the left of Transport:boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | bus  | airplane    | boat | scooter    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

