.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
Beverage: fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
Pet: turtle, goldfish, frog, rabbit
1. Beverage:water != Pet:turtle##6
2. Pet:goldfish != Beverage:sprite##6
3. Pet:frog is on the left or right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##3
4. Pet:goldfish == Beverage:fanta##1
5. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left of Pet:goldfish##1
6. Beverage:fanta is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:turtle is on the far left or far right##3
8. Pet:frog is somewhere to the left of Pet:rabbit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | water       | hot-chocolate  | fanta  | sprite |
| Job        | frog | rabbit | goldfish | turtle  |

