2. Pet:guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of Beverage:almond-milk##5
3. Beverage:tea != Pet:guinea-pig##6
4. Beverage:tea is somewhere to the right of Beverage:almond-milk##5
5. Beverage:iced-tea is on the right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
6. Pet:snake is somewhere to the left of Beverage:tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | hedgehog | snake     | goldfish |
| Transport   | hot-chocolate     | iced-tea    | almond-milk | tea    |

